detaileddescription.para:
Inflates (in one of two sides) given mesh region, putting given vertices in such positions to make smooth surface inside verts-region, but sharp on its boundary; 

verts



must not include all vertices of a mesh connected component Generated from function MR::inflate. Parameter mesh can not be null. It is a single object. Parameter verts can not be null. It is a single object. Parameter settings can not be null. It is a single object.
